r grid, it looks a little distorted and thats a very popular design component at the moment.</p><p>An element that is conveniently used in this layout is the Feature Section. Its not only a very quickly customizable block, it also takes care of responsiveness for you. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vce-row-container\"><div class=\"vce-row vce-element--has-background vce-row--col-gap-30 vce-row-equal-height vce-row-content--top\" data-vce-full-width=\"true\" id=\"el-093dc7ed\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-093dc7ed\"><div class=\"vce-content-background-container\"></div><div class=\"vce-row-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\"><div class=\"vce-col vce-col--md-auto vce-col--xs-1 vce-col--xs-last vce-col--xs-first vce-col--sm-last vce-col--sm-first vce-col--md-last vce-col--lg-last vce-col--xl-last vce-col--md-first vce-col--lg-first vce-col--xl-first\" id=\"el-3d4f6a07\"><div class=\"vce-col-inner\" data-vce-do-apply=\"border margin background  el-3d4f6a07\"><div class=\"vce-col-content\" data-vce-element-content=\"true\" data-vce-do-apply=\"padding el-3d4f6a07\"><div class=\"vce-single-image-container vce-single-image--align-center\"><div class=\"vce vce-single-image-wrapper\" id=\"el-ed229819\" data-vce-do-apply=\"all el-ed229819\"><figure><a href=\"https://getenjoyhq.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"vce-single-image-inner vce-single-image--absolute\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.9524%; width: 840px;\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"vce-single-image\" width=\"840\" height=\"470\" src=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/enjoy-hq-840x470.png\" srcset=\"https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/enjoy-hq-320x179.png 320w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/enjoy-hq-480x269.png 480w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/enjoy-hq-800x448.png 800w,https://visualcomposer.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/enjoy-hq-840x470.png 840w\" data-img-src=\"htt